Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见了 宁子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…已经不记得我了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是瓦尔基莉亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:01:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫做“真子”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那样叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1107号 鹰鸟小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟是1107号？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧 我说过她在这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快表扬我 千怜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.76,0:02:23.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1107号 你没有权利逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的性命归我所有
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(part-a)
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(title)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(640,482)\c&HE9E4E3&}魔 女 猎 手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 没希望了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在只剩下这一手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 村上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有话要跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮助魔女出谋划策的人就是你么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了 放我一条生路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.56,0:03:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是看她们可怜才帮她们一把
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事儿和我一点关系都没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.17,0:03:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以求求你饶命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.28,0:03:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.78,0:03:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我也真是烂好人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来可以溜之大吉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:19.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过只要挂起了 即使是瓦尔基莉亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.14,0:03:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么啊 我该按哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.71,0:03:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.06,0:03:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.49,0:03:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.92,0:03:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得明明已经杀了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非强制弹出 否则她死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.80,0:03:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那强制弹出她好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 让她活着会给我们找麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.29,0:03:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 初菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你留下来想帮我们 但反而害了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 她们只不过想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为没有让她们活下去的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且让她们活在世上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.48,0:04:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我们会有潜在威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.06,0:04:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这全是为了你们的利益
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.43,0:04:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们有没有考虑因此被杀的魔法使们的感受啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你弄死虫子的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:25.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会一一考虑它们的立场么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.34,0:04:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本是两码事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法使不是虫子 也是活生生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:34.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是人类众生平等么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.06,0:04:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何生命都有自己的立场
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯有自己的生命才是最珍贵的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 你错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:48.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多说无益 除了1107号全部杀掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但之前说好不杀宁子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有听懂我的命令么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:04:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让我浪费口舌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家趁现在快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.34,0:05:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少蹬鼻子上脸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.30,0:05:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要闭着嘴跟我们走就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碰小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对千怜干了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你们了 快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她太碍事了 快动手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁子 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.99,0:06:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.19,0:06:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.65,0:06:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别把其他人都想得和你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 有的生命比自己的性命更重要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上同学 村上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.71,0:06:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了大家 帮不了你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:35.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢 村上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上同学 村上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈…奈波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么啊 谁是奈波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:51.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是留存在你记忆里的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你走投无路的时候 就会显现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在确实是走投无路了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 他出血太多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经出现幻觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说话 只需思考就可以和我交流
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我浏览了监视员的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了令研究所惧怕的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惧怕？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 一个是1107号 鹰鸟小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.53,0:07:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一个是黑羽宁子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑羽？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她拥有比瓦尔基莉亚更强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她的力量很不稳定没有人可以控制她
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以研究所把她封印了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我教你如何解除封印
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这种方法对于现在的宁子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,99.9%的可能会失败导致她死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是想度过这次难关
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有赌一下这个方法了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:03.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 意识越来越…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 奈波
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上 振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个混蛋 居然这样对村上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.57,0:08:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香澄 你这个混账
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再做无用功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你除了破坏一无是处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.45,0:08:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在连这么没用的魔法都用不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁想成为魔法使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.31,0:08:35.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他们强行改造我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.65,0:08:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为什么我们就要失去一切啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香澄…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:46.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我有力量的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量 你是有的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:54.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑羽比瓦尔基莉亚还要强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上同学 你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:08:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奈波告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除黑羽封印的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是按下拘束具最上方的那个按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.02,0:09:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想按就按 她只会融化而死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,99.9%会失败的按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.40,0:09:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我按不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 快杀掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔基莉亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁子 对不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.98,0:09:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法拒绝千怜的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不了魔法了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是你想的难道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不见 九所长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么会知道这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据GPS信号定位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个装置打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何 失去了引以为傲的力量的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他名为伊尼夏莱尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(700,660)}initializer
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他面前一切魔法都会被中和
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把1107号交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 1107号也不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:41.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 就擦伤一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少废话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此 我也中和了她的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可你没告诉我她会瞬间移动
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.35,0:10:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美树 这都是因为你调查得不够充分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 少把责任推到我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.19,0:10:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.74,0:10:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.64,0:10:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒醒 村上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:02.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他心跳停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.82,0:11:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下一点意义都没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上不在了 我活着还有什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.57,0:11:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说过就算我忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会记着我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能换来村上同学活着该有多好
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(part-b)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要这样 村上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 还有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初菜 你已经恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是心跳停止了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该还可以救他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 请快点动手 快把村上救活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:55.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过用这种能力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.23,0:11:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的身体会融化的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.19,0:12:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可信号塔的事 我还欠他一个人情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没他的话 也没法搞到镇死剂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:05.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试一试
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在身体融化完之前把他治好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:15.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口愈合了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点难 明明伤口已经愈合了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可心脏却没有跳动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.43,0:12:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能 我头一次挂起了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.31,0:12:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.34,0:12:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来我不是白白送死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初菜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.47,0:12:43.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上没活过来 初菜也融掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香澄 别在那儿发傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快给他做心脏按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.10,0:12:59.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.99,0:13:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上 拜托了 快喘口气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.80,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.00,0:13:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我晕过去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.08,0:13:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是 刚才你死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初菜救了你 用自己的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:45.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是初菜？为什么你要这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.62,0:13:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我搭上自己的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结局都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.37,0:13:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女必须死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是魔女猎手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(700,660)}hexenjagd
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.47,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}注：hexenjagd，原指中世纪的巫女审判猎杀行为，这里仅仅套用来命名组织
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了阻止研究所的计划而成立的对抗组织
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要杀魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们明明什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:11.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要魔法使还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.62,0:14:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拘束具里的朵拉希尔就会在她们体内一直成长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朵拉希尔 你是指那个像史莱姆一样的生物么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当它们孵化的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:25.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会完全吞噬掉魔女的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成真正的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.00,0:14:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是只会食人的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会变成怪物？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:39.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但真正危险的不是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是1107号
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.27,0:14:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:59.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不在我面前现身 怜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.10,0:15:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是怜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切生命都是没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在怜奈病逝以前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怜奈的身体可以说是残次品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她的脑和心脏没有受损
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不需要肉体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要给脑供给氧气和营养成分的话她就不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为什么没有活过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么她的灵魂不在大脑里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:34.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做才能让她再次苏生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生命到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的真正目的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:44.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是创造出可以支配这个星球的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而从魔女体内培养的那些朵拉希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:53.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在数千分之一的概率下孵化出的格拉尼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.71,0:15:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是我们要创造的完全生命体所必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:03.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是怜奈 我叫鹰鸟小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你原本的身体是怜奈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本的身体？那我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球上的人类全部是外星人创造的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.45,0:16:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是调查遗迹的结论
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时外星人在人类的基因结构里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下了可以重设地球的机关
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重设…地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.61,0:16:30.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而灭亡人类的开关
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟她？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹰鸟小鸟身上的格拉尼孵卵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全体生命的细胞都会融化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.42,0:16:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地球就会变成没有生物的死星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种说法也太荒谬了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们本来也是研究所的一分子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.31,0:16:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来知晓了他们的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了杀死鹰鸟小鸟 我们袭击了运输车
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了载有小鸟的运输车
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的运输车也被卷了进去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此我们不仅丢失了小鸟的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还损失了一名同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.61,0:17:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说我们必须死就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.77,0:17:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少说蠢话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说也不会马上就孵卵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许吧 可能是一年以后也可能是两年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是也有可能就在明天
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们都快用完镇死剂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.92,0:17:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连一个星期都活不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:37.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么狗屁对抗组织
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的所作所为和九有什么不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对不会放弃希望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.97,0:17:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你们也不要放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实在一周之内孵卵基本是不可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.17,0:17:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随他们去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说追查1107号是当前的头等大事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.98,0:18:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的不错 但九的藏身处要怎么找
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九的位置 我们可以确保
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香澄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:11.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给你了 香澄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:19.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然 待我黑上研究所的数据库
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把他给揪出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.97,0:18:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做个交易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们找出九的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.87,0:18:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为交换条件 你们一并带我们过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:32.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且我们也尝试过入侵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过遇上魔女的阻碍…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 别把我和你们的水准相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.45,0:18:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香澄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 交给我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.03,0:18:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九的数据被消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:19:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了 原来是对面魔法使的小把戏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少瞧不起人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数据慢慢恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害 这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.05,0:19:16.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你们就跟过来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是杀死1107号这个决定不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,香澄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前和奇佳子战斗过的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.28,0:19:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个湖边附近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九以他母亲的名义购置的别墅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.22,0:19:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好 香澄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,速度跟上 外面有直升机等着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳奈在这里等我们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.19,0:19:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 小鸟就靠你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一定会带小鸟回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 初菜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给予我的生命 我不会白白浪费的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你脊髓里的格拉尼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给它吞噬了怜奈的脑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以格拉尼里应该寄宿着怜奈的意识
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.34,0:20:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看起来没有成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要将格拉尼转移到了新的宿主上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.44,0:20:24.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了自己之外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切的生命都没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是怜奈不同
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.99,0:20:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论牺牲多少生命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都要让怜奈的意识复生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.99,0:20:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦尔基莉亚的生命也没有意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可她看起来很喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前我救过她一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是她因此感恩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但对我来说 只是计划上需要她而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对她不存在任何的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 但还是喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难…难道要孵卵了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.97,0:21:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是无限之光 执掌生命之光
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(550,660)}Ain-soph Aur
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.77,0:21:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs36}注：Ain-soph Aur，具体请自行wiki卡巴拉生命树详解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当它覆盖地球的时候 生命将灭绝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有赶上么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.44,0:21:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起毫不知情马上要面对死亡的数十亿人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可幸福多了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鸟…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(ED)
